    "created_at": "2016-08-26T19:51:29Z",
    "updated_at": "2016-08-26T19:51:29Z",
    "body": "That should be sufficient in theory, but `_debugWaitConnect` is intended to be an internal mechanism. Is there a way for you to pass flags (`--debug-brk`) to Node and let Node handle this internal business? I am not too familiar with how Electron embeds Node, so I am not sure if this is possible.\n"
