    "created_at": "2016-08-26T20:53:12Z",
    "updated_at": "2016-08-26T20:53:12Z",
    "body": "> Is there a way for you to pass flags (--debug-brk) to Node and let Node handle this internal business?\n\nHmm, yeah, the node integration in Electron is done via calling into `node::CreateEnvironment`, and the `--debug-brk` argument seems to be parsed via calling `node::Start`.\n"
